'''Júlio Silvão Tavares''' (yavutse 1959), niUmukinnyi wa firime muri [[Kapu Veri|Cape Verdean]] . <ref>http://www.filmstarts.de/personen/785992.html</ref> <ref>http://cinafrica.letras.ufrj.br/index.php/filmes/cabo-verde/147-julio-silvao-tavares</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Kuva mu 1979, yize umuco gakondo wa Cape-verdean, aho yashinze Itsinda rya Theatre Experimental igihe yari producer numuyobozi wa gahunda yumuco 'Dragoeiro' yatambutse kuri Televisão de Cabo Verde (TCV) kuva 1993 kugeza 1997. Kuva 1994 kugeza 1996, Tavares yari umuyobozi wa gahunda yumuco 'Articultura' kuri Rádio de Cabo Verde (RCV). <ref>https://www.tieff.org/en/directors/julio-silvao-tavares/</ref> Ni n'umuyobozi wa sosiyete ikora firime yitwa 'Silvão-Produção Filmes' yashinze mu 2004. <ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.person.julio-silvao-tavares.8749.html</ref>

Hagati aho, yakoze firime ''O Desafio'' mu 1999. Mu 2005, yerekanwe bwa mbere muri firime na ''Batuque, Alma de um Povo'' .Ku itsinda rya muzika rya batuque Raiz di Tambarina, n'imizi y'iyi njyana ya muzika i Santiago, Cape Verde . <ref>http://www.larepubliquedespyrenees.fr/2010/06/09/soiree-musicale-capverdienne,140991.php</ref> <ref>http://www.marfilmes.com/en/africadocs/batuque.htm</ref> Iyi filime yerekanwe i Lisbonne mu Gushyingo 2010, nyuma yerekanwa mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime. <ref>https://archive.is/20120707221120/http://africainthepicture.nl/2007/en/program/filmsA-Z/13/Batuque/_Batuque,_a_alma_de_um_povo.html</ref> <ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Africa_in_Motion</ref>


